data.description: Check out this hidden gem in Boiling Springs! Tucked away in a clu-de-sac, this home is in a non-HOA neighborhood. As you enter into a spacious living room, you’ll find warm wood floors and an inviting space. The master bedroom at the front of the house features a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms have generous closets and the same wood floors. The hall opens into a large dining room that has adjoining 2nd bathroom with new tiles walk-in shower, and the laundry room. Moving to the kitchen, you’ll find lots of recent upgrades. New cabinets, backsplash, tile floor, all new appliances, including the sink, and range hood. With this home, the recently replaced water heater and washer and dryer come included. Recent upgrades also include 3 new ceiling fans to keep you cool in the summer. Large enclosed attic gives plenty of storage to this home!
